<Layout
  title="How To Build A Mobile App For Your Front-Commerce Website"
  description="Want to build a mobile app for your Front-Commerce website, without hundreds of thousands of dollars of investment? MobiLoud makes it easy. See how it works inside."
>
  <Nav />

